{"title":"外国谚语","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":5,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"外国谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（罗马尼亚）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　正义战无不胜，真理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高于一切。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　哪里有懦怯，那里有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耻辱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　宁可穷而有志，不可"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富而失节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　没有舵手的船会沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　声誉比金子更可贵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　人正不怕影子歪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　骄傲的朋友是愚蠢和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫困。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　懒惰对于人好比铁生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了锈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　没有真理的人叫喊得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　阿谀奉承，等于半个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辱骂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　为别人掘陷井，掉下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去的正是他自己。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}